{"title":"Time to update Zwift: the neon lights of Neokyo are now on with Makuri Islands expansion","link":"https://bikerumor.com/time-to-update-zwift-the-neon-lights-of-neokyo-are-now-on-with-makuri-islands-expansion/","date":1637265600000,"content":"<div id=\"readability-page-1\" class=\"page\"><div><a href=\"https://s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/11/18142816/Zwift-Neokyo-map-update-virtual-training-4.jpg\" data-fancybox=\"\"><img width=\"800\" height=\"450\" src=\"https://s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/11/18142816/Zwift-Neokyo-map-update-virtual-training-4-800x450.jpg\" alt=\"\" loading=\"lazy\" srcset=\"https://s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/11/18142816/Zwift-Neokyo-map-update-virtual-training-4-800x450.jpg 800w, https://s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/11/18142816/Zwift-Neokyo-map-update-virtual-training-4-297x167.jpg 297w, https://s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/11/18142816/Zwift-Neokyo-map-update-virtual-training-4-120x68.jpg 120w, https://s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/11/18142816/Zwift-Neokyo-map-update-virtual-training-4-768x432.jpg 768w, https://s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/11/18142816/Zwift-Neokyo-map-update-virtual-training-4.jpg 1200w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 800px) 100vw, 800px\"></a><header></header><p>Support us! BikeRumor may earn a small commission from affiliate links in this article. <a href=\"https://bikerumor.com/privacy\" target=\"_blank\">Learn more</a>.</p></div><div role=\"main\"><article id=\"post-278811\" role=\"article\" itemscope=\"\" itemtype=\"http://schema.org/BlogPosting\"><section itemprop=\"text\"><p>It’s been <a href=\"https://bikerumor.com/new-zwift-neokyo-makuri-island-map/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">teased</a> for almost a month, but Zwift’s latest map expansion is finally open for <del>business</del> riding. Modeled after the big cities of Japan, Neokyo offers a fun, vibrant feel plus eight new routes.</p><p><a href=\"https://s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/11/18142811/Zwift-Neokyo-map-update-virtual-training-2.jpg\"><img loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/11/18142811/Zwift-Neokyo-map-update-virtual-training-2.jpg\" alt=\"Zwift Neokyo update\" width=\"1200\" height=\"675\" srcset=\"https://s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/11/18142811/Zwift-Neokyo-map-update-virtual-training-2.jpg 1200w, https://s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/11/18142811/Zwift-Neokyo-map-update-virtual-training-2-297x167.jpg 297w, https://s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/11/18142811/Zwift-Neokyo-map-update-virtual-training-2-800x450.jpg 800w, https://s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/11/18142811/Zwift-Neokyo-map-update-virtual-training-2-120x68.jpg 120w, https://s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/11/18142811/Zwift-Neokyo-map-update-virtual-training-2-768x432.jpg 768w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1200px) 100vw, 1200px\"></a></p><p>Hidden within the world of the Makuri Islands and doubling it in size, Neokyo offers a completely different experience with huge buildings, wild neon lighting, and a dazzling arcade that’s comically filled with “arcade games”—bikes on stationary trainers in front of a screen.</p><p>In total, there are eight new routes, with the longest offering 20.2 miles and 2,261ft of climbing. Neokyo is fairly compact, so the longer routes will loop around a few times, sometimes climbing into the rooftops.</p><div><p><b>RAILWAYS AND ROOFTOPS&nbsp;</b></p><p>Take to the upper city where you will race along city railways and rooftops.</p></div><div><p>Distance: 3.8 mi // 6.1 km, Elevation Gain: 226 ft // 68.9 m</p></div><div><p><b>ROOFTOP RENDEZVOUS&nbsp;</b></p><p>Feel the burn as you climb to the top of Neokyo, scaling rooftops and monorails on the way.</p></div><div><p>Distance: 2.3 mi // 3.7 km, Elevation Gain: 16.7 ft // 5.1 m</p></div><div><p><b>NEON FLATS&nbsp;</b></p><p>Paint the town as you dominate three sprints along this flat route through the city.</p></div><div><p>Distance: 8.9 mi // 14.4 km, Elevation Gain: 474.7 ft // 144.7 m</p></div><div><p><b>SPRINTER’S PLAYGROUND&nbsp;</b></p><p>Keep that heart racing as you complete four sprints in a single route.</p></div><div><p>Distance: 7.6 mi // 12.3 km, Elevation Gain: 157 ft // 51.5 m</p></div><div><p><b>NEOKYO ALL-NIGHTER&nbsp;</b></p><p>Explore everything that Neokyo has to offer including four sprints and a KOM along this challenging route.</p></div><div><p>Distance: 15.1 mi // 24.3 km, Elevation Gain: 562.3 ft // 171.3 m</p></div><div><p><b>SLEEPLESS CITY&nbsp;</b></p><p>Make your way through the heart of the city as you wind along this fast route.</p></div><div><p>Distance: 5.7 mi // 9.2 km, Elevation Gain: 268 ft // 81.7 m</p></div><div><p><b>WANDERING FLATS&nbsp;</b></p><p>This long flatter route will take you from the scenic countryside to the bustling city.</p></div><div><p>Distance: 16 mi // 25.7 km, Elevation Gain: 866 ft // 264 m</p></div><div><p><b>TEMPLES AND TOWERS&nbsp;</b></p><p>From downtown rooftops to mystical temples, grind to complete three KOM’s in a single route.</p></div><div><p>Distance: 20.2 mi // 32.5 km, Elevation Gain: 2,261.2 ft // 689.2 m</p></div><p><a href=\"https://s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/11/18142823/Zwift-Neokyo-map-update-virtual-training-7.jpg\"><img loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/11/18142823/Zwift-Neokyo-map-update-virtual-training-7.jpg\" alt=\"Zwift Neokyo update nya cat\" width=\"1200\" height=\"675\" srcset=\"https://s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/11/18142823/Zwift-Neokyo-map-update-virtual-training-7.jpg 1200w, https://s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/11/18142823/Zwift-Neokyo-map-update-virtual-training-7-297x167.jpg 297w, https://s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/11/18142823/Zwift-Neokyo-map-update-virtual-training-7-800x450.jpg 800w, https://s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/11/18142823/Zwift-Neokyo-map-update-virtual-training-7-120x68.jpg 120w, https://s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/11/18142823/Zwift-Neokyo-map-update-virtual-training-7-768x432.jpg 768w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1200px) 100vw, 1200px\"></a></p><p><a href=\"https://s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/11/18142818/Zwift-Neokyo-map-update-virtual-training-5.jpg\"><img loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/11/18142818/Zwift-Neokyo-map-update-virtual-training-5.jpg\" alt=\"Zwift Neokyo update thing?\" width=\"1200\" height=\"675\" srcset=\"https://s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/11/18142818/Zwift-Neokyo-map-update-virtual-training-5.jpg 1200w, https://s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/11/18142818/Zwift-Neokyo-map-update-virtual-training-5-297x167.jpg 297w, https://s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/11/18142818/Zwift-Neokyo-map-update-virtual-training-5-800x450.jpg 800w, https://s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/11/18142818/Zwift-Neokyo-map-update-virtual-training-5-120x68.jpg 120w, https://s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/11/18142818/Zwift-Neokyo-map-update-virtual-training-5-768x432.jpg 768w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1200px) 100vw, 1200px\"></a></p><p>The update for Zwift is available now—just plan ahead, it’s a big one.</p></section></article></div></div>","author":"Zach Overholt","siteTitle":"Bikerumor","siteHash":"49f427af0a926f4232eb837006841d7242e153e3afbb590f32e4b104ea3e2718","entryHash":"12bdeabe816b3886eb437d2597e8d0450a0a78f60a82770f802be894647f2883","category":"Cycling"}